name: Po's special package
description: Po's special package is a secret digital artefact made from nostalgic 90's tv show Teletubbies’ atmosphere. The 4-frame-loop by brazilian graphic designer Renata Sá (@rntza) is a fusion between 2018 print experiments and 2021 digital image distortion work.  [Digital Graphics Interchange Format File 1667 x 1668 pixels 2021.7.5]
